price: 52. "Am I not better than this one [Mûsâ (Moses)] who is despicable and can scarcely express himself clearly?
arabic: أَمۡ أَنَا۠ خَيۡرٞ مِّنۡ هَٰذَا ٱلَّذِي هُوَ مَهِينٞ وَلَا يَكَادُ يُبِينُ
